div.p: JobFeed is our weekly jobs email that lists all the newly advertised permanent and temporary teaching positions in NSW public schools as well as non-school based teaching positions. JobFeed also features new opportunities that may enhance your teaching career. Subscribe to JobFeed to have the newly advertised positions delivered to your inbox every Wednesday. Alternatively, download our JobFeed app, which not only lists all the advertised positions, but shows the location of each position on a map and, for rural and remote schools, indicates the applicable benefits and incentives. Download the JobFeed app from the App Store or Google Play.
Note: There are a range of incentives that may apply to teaching positions in rural or remote areas of NSW.
